---
title: Mediterranean-Style Bocconcini and Shrimp Orzo with Garlic Bread
description: Tangy mixed olives and creamy bocconcini pearls come together to bring bold flavour to this savoury, Mediterranean-style shrimp orzo. A side of garlic bread to scoop up every bite makes the meal complete!
